  Boot configuration:       {1}
  Available configurations: {2}

  Action: Specify a boot configuration that actually exists.

One or more required files are missing.
  Machine: {0}
  Files:   {1}

  Action: Create the required files (perhaps with vm-realize), or edit the boot configuration
          to remove references to the files.

One or more required files and nmdm(4) devices are missing.
  Machine:      {0}
  Files:        {1}
  NMDM Devices: {2}

  Action: Create the required files (perhaps with vm-realize), or edit the boot configuration
          to remove references to the files. Additionally, nmdm(4) devices are automatically
          created upon opening. The fact that an nmdm(4) device does not exist may indicate
          that the nmdm kernel module needs to be loaded.

One or more disks are missing an attachment.
  Machine: {0}
  Device:  {1}

  Action: Edit the boot configuration so that a file/disk is attached to all drives that require one.
